            <a href="https://x.com/tuliosousapro" target="_blank"
               class="w-full border-2 border-purple-600 text-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-600 hover:text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-center block transition-all duration-300">
               ùïè Connect on X
